        <Desc>We develop services to meet the changing mental health needs in our community. Highest Horizon Support Services offers a platform for individuals to express themselves and receive assistance. Our aim is to improve mental well-being by providing education support and empathy to enable lasting positive transformations in the lives of those we help. In 2024 we organized quarterly events to support the community such as Clothing Drives Back-to-School Drives Christmas Giveaways for supported families and Spring Community Events tailored to our service recipients. These events incurred a total expense of $6500.</Desc>
